beer.beer_description:
KRAMPUS KRINGLE
’Tis the season for merriment and celebration, sometimes sprinkled with an (un)healthy dose of debauchery and indulgence. Not ones to rain on holiday cheer, we’ve conjured up a Christmas Ale aged in a combination of bourbon barrels, rum barrels, and amburana wood, finished with an infusion of festive spices. Time to get cheery!

Packaged specially for Beer Cartel's 2024 Advent Calendar.
